C++                             C
#include <string>		        #include <string.h>                 <-- different
#include "class.h"              #include "class.h"                  <-- same
string1 = string2               strcpy(string2, string1)
int main() { }                  void main() { }
C array, or vector object       C array only
const                           #DEFINE                             <-- not really true, but well...


TERMINOLOGY
-----------
Member function =   method
Member data     =   instance variable 
Copy constructor ~ memberwise assignment
static          <>  automatic variable/object

